title: #92Noon! Gorg/Gleeman/Johnson/Hendricks
description: Kevin Gorg stops by to talk Wild, Aaron Gleeman talks about the faltering Twins, Ron Johnson brings some football discussion before new Wild forward and former Blaine Bengal Matt Hendricks calls in to talk about joining his hometown team!
